c: 23
v: 50
t: "Soni twantesile Mwanache jwa Maryam kwisa soni Mamagwe kuŵa chisimosimo (chakulosya ukombosi Wetu, wakomboleka ŵakongwe kuŵeleka mwanache mwangali kusimana ni ŵalume), ni twajuyiye ŵanaŵaŵilio pachikwesya chakutamilichika ni ntunjelele, chachakwete soni achitutumule (pa Baitul Muqaddas)"